import mongoose from "mongoose";

const resourceSchema = new mongoose.Schema({
	"Resource #": String,
	"Organization Title": String,
	"Resource Type": String,
	"Grants Current Status": String,
	"Current US Resident/Country": String,
	City: String,
	State: String,
	Birthdate: String,
	Race: String,
	Dependents: String,
	"Acceptable Use Of Funds": String,
	"Are You Considered A:": String,
	"How Long Have You Worked In The Industry": String,
	"What Genre Of Music Do You Play? ": String,
	"Proof Of Musicianship/Industry Work": String,
	"Org Membership": String,
	"Proof Of Lost Income": String,
	"Primary Source Of Income? ": String,
	"Gross Annual Income": String,
	"Music- Income Amount": String,
	"Financial Documents Required": String,
	"How Have You Been Affected By COVID?": String,
	"Healthcare Related Issue": String,
	"Proof Of Emergency": "",
	"Crises Type?": "",
	"Other Request": "",
	NOTES: "Either 2 years industry or member of AGM + Proof Of Loss",
	"OTHER NOTES": "",
});

//const Resource = mongoose.model("Resource", resourceSchema);

export default resourceSchema;
